sentences.english: Or such mangling can be performed automatically after an executable is created.
sentences.chinese: 或者也可以等到可执行文件生成之后再自动化切碎。

sentences.english: System was out of memory, executable file was corrupt, or relocations were invalid.
sentences.chinese: 系统内存不足，可执行文件损错误或重新定位无效。

sentences.english: The fully-qualified path to the executable must be provided.
sentences.chinese: 必须提供可执行文件的完全限定路径。

sentences.english: Enable to run a customized executable at shut-down.
sentences.chinese: 启用关闭时运行定制的可执行文件。

sentences.english: C is a compiled language, which creates fast and efficient executable files.
sentences.chinese: 是一种编译语言，可以产生快速有效的可执行文件。

sentences.english: You have to set an executable to add to the QuickBar first.
sentences.chinese: 要添加到快捷栏您必须先选择一个可执行文件。

sentences.english: But do not assume that because you have acted naturally your product is without flaw.
sentences.chinese: 但是不要认为你能行文自然，你的作品就毫无瑕疵。

sentences.english: Swifty Xena Pro can extract uncompressed SWF files from executables.
sentences.chinese: 迅速出没亲能提取压缩档案瑞士法郎从可执行文件。

sentences.english: Applications using them are called dynamic executables.
sentences.chinese: 使用它们的应用程序作为动态可执行文件。

sentences.english: This really provides the central rhetorical base for Milton's Lycidas.
sentences.chinese: 这为弥尔顿的《利西达斯》提供了行文基调。

sentences.english: I got lost in your rather diffuse essay.
sentences.chinese: 你的文章行文冗赘，弄得我有点糊涂了。

sentences.english: This is the absolute pathname of the executable that started the process.
sentences.chinese: 此参数为进程可执行文件的绝对路径。

sentences.english: Processes are live entities executing the instructions of an executable file.
sentences.chinese: 进程是执行可执行文件的指令的动态实体。

sentences.english: It is an effective method to protect software by packing Portable Executable(PE) files.
sentences.chinese: 对可执行文件加壳是保护软件的一种有效方法。

sentences.english: Until somebody notices that you're sharing an inordinate number of executable files.
sentences.chinese: 直到有人发现你们正在分享数量过多的可执行文件。

sentences.english: Walla , your ASP Project has just been exported to an executable file.
sentences.chinese: 沃拉，您的ASP项目刚刚被出口到一个可执行文件。
